        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Door Matrix Pricing"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Matrix Pricing was developed for the UK and Australia, this method for pricing Doors is performed with a size range per Material. Matrix pricing was added to facilitate this method. It is typically only enabled overseas, but can be turned on by adding MatrixPricing=1 to the Cabinet Vision\\Solid_10_0\\Catalogs\\Door branch in the registry."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Editing the Windows Registry is only recommended for those familiar with the Windows Registry. Always make a backup of the Registry prior to editing. One wrong entry to could make it impossible to Open Cabinet Vision or even Windows. Be very careful!"
        },
        {
